Package: canriskBridge
Type: Package
Title: Evagene Integration Example - CanRisk 2.0 Pedigree Export
Version: 0.1.0
Description: A minimal Evagene REST API integration that fetches a pedigree
    as a ##CanRisk 2.0 file, saves it to disk, and optionally opens
    canrisk.org for upload to the BOADICEA assessment.  Distributed as an
    example; not a validated clinical tool.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.3.0)
Imports:
    httr2 (>= 1.0.0)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.2.0)
